OL,3,CFriends of man who drowned prepare for
OL,4,Cmarathon cycle ride in his memory
OL,6,FFriends of a man who died after
OL,7,Fswimming off the coast of Wirral in
OL,8,F2022 are to cycle the entire coast of
OL,9,FWales and on to New Brighton to raise
OL,10,Fmoney for the Royal National Lifeboat
OL,11,FInstitution (RNLI).
OL,13,FHaydn Griffiths from Wigan was an
OL,14,Fathletic 23-year-old who had extensive
OL,15,Fknowledge of the water. But he
OL,16,Fdisappeared off the coast near Hoylake
OL,17,Fin July 2022 while swimming on a first
OL,18,Fdate.
