OL,3,CFriends of man who drowned prepare for
OL,4,Cmarathon cycle ride in his memory
OL,6,FVolunteer RNLI lifeboat crews from
OL,7,FHoylake and New Brighton searched for
OL,8,FHaydn, but his body was recovered five
OL,9,Fdays later.
OL,11,FSince his death, Haydn's family and
OL,12,Ffriends have been raising funds for
OL,13,Fthe RNLI in his memory as well as
OL,14,Fawareness of the charity's lifesaving
OL,15,Fwater safety advice.
OL,17,FNow, four friends who he knew through
OL,18,Fsailing are gearing up to take on a
OL,19,F530-mile cycling challenge taking in
OL,20,Fthe coast of Wales on the anniversary
OL,21,Fof the search for Haydn.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
