OL,3,CFriends of man who drowned prepare for
OL,4,Cmarathon cycle ride in his memory
OL,6,FThe ride will start in Chepstow in
OL,7,FWales and go from south to north,
OL,8,Ffinishing at New Brighton on the
OL,9,FWirral ` a route which includes more
OL,10,Fthan 8,000 metres of ascent,
OL,11,Fequivalent to climbing Mount Everest.
OL,13,FThe group has set a target of raising
OL,14,F#5,000 for the RNLI as a thank you for
OL,15,Feverything they did in the search for
OL,16,FHaydn and for their life-saving
OL,17,Fefforts over the last 200 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
