OL,3,CFriends of man who drowned prepare for
OL,4,Cmarathon cycle ride in his memory
OL,6,FOne of the friends taking part in the
OL,7,Fchallenge, Sarah Jarman, said: "I am
OL,8,Fsuper excited about this challenge.
OL,9,FThe RNLI is a fabulous cause that I
OL,10,Fthink really embraces Haydn's
OL,11,Finterests.
OL,13,F"By taking this on together, I hope
OL,14,Fthat we will be able to celebrate
OL,15,FHaydn's life and spirit and mark his
OL,16,Ftragic loss in a positive way that I
OL,17,Fhope he would be proud of."
