OL,3,CFriends of man who drowned prepare for
OL,4,Cmarathon cycle ride in his memory
OL,6,FCatherine Jones, RNLI Community
OL,7,FManager, said: "The challenge these
OL,8,Ffour friends are taking on in memory
OL,9,Fof Haydn to support the lifesaving
OL,10,Fwork of the RNLI is incredible.
OL,12,F"Haydn's legacy has already been
OL,13,Fraising awareness and vital funds to
OL,14,Fhelp the charity which worked
OL,15,Ftirelessly to search for him, and this
OL,16,Fis another fitting tribute. The money
OL,17,Fthis great team raises will help our
OL,18,Fvolunteers in the work they do around
OL,19,Fthe coast."
